{"tid":159210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想識個麵包店女仔，有咩辦法？","createTime":"2017-03-16T20:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T14:11:39.000Z","uid":71740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"955062f422cc6fe2a19987131f58b46e9c9f80d3","tid":159210,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T20:53:10.000Z","msg":"最近成日去間Yamazaki買麵包，<br />\n個囡囡店員幾正下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為想吃果款果間冇，所以要訂，<br />\n今日留左個手提俾佢，叫佢覆我遲幾日會唔會拿到訂既麵包，<br />\n佢最後用公司電話打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩辦法可以拿佢WhatsApp 同多d 同佢chat下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4d6fb9f65b176fe381a61ba38a8d16fdc5af93","tid":159210,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:10:40.000Z","msg":"用語音錄可能有錯字，講真你要留意下佢對你有冇笑，你問佢野嗰陣佢有冇心答你，如果你覺得OK其實你直接問佢拎電話已經OK，好過你這頭遮路又唔夠膽咁拎佢電話，如果佢對你都有少少好感，佢實肯俾個電話你"},{"pid":"025573057b8c895d6f78b67dced29f5a26588d6d","tid":159210,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:13:27.000Z","msg":"小姐，你鐘唔鐘意法式長棍包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （磁性聲音"},{"pid":"d0d25bb3c27b8e5ede1736dcd3badd760ac179f7","tid":159210,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用語音錄可能有錯字，講真你要留意下佢對你有冇笑，你問佢野嗰陣佢有冇心答你，如果你覺得OK其實你直接問佢拎電話已經OK，好過你這頭遮路又唔夠膽咁拎佢電話，如果佢對你都有少少好感，佢實肯俾個電話你</blockquote><br />\n都見過幾次啦，有傾幾句有講有笑咁，仲好好禮貌，但我驚係我錯覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者人地工作需要對客態度好<br />\n未試過直接問電話&hellip;<br />\n毒l最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黎緊應該仲有機會去訂包，或者我留張卡片俾佢叫佢直接WhatsApp我"},{"pid":"0e03baac050f5971b7654fe7da96912a2ff5c583","tid":159210,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小姐，你鐘唔鐘意法式長棍包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （磁性聲音</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次試下係舖頭拿條包調戲下佢先"},{"pid":"254a1837e74b710dd3cbbeae01d82b58fcd6c893","tid":159210,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:28:45.000Z","msg":"下次搵機會摸下手仔  再同佢單下眼"},{"pid":"c36ba96851559ae3bbcae907696af0dcd37704da","tid":159210,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:29:27.000Z","msg":"收購Yamazaki 之後你想點識就點識"},{"pid":"e6b12b4719dfa9dde06acc12dafb8fd110e053e8","tid":159210,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T21:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小姐，你鐘唔鐘意法式長棍包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （磁性聲音</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次試下係舖頭拿條包調戲下佢先</blockquote><br />\n留名新聞見"},{"pid":"57d1679b2040b669e9a8cacb630980b3455aa090","tid":159210,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T22:52:28.000Z","msg":"唔好搞我條女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155bbd8e382b6bc164e2d77fddde07c65f689956","tid":159210,"uid":17520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T23:08:11.000Z","msg":"食多啲麵包"},{"pid":"6b53495256304b0e76a2ebfae218381c2ea0a54e","tid":159210,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:26:27.000Z","msg":"同佢講想食佢隻包"},{"pid":"c948f37fc41270c07148480701fbedb5243f768d","tid":159210,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T00:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小姐，你鐘唔鐘意法式長棍包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （磁性聲音</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次試下係舖頭拿條包調戲下佢先</blockquote><br />\